class:: Delay1
summary:: Single sample delay.
related:: Classes/Delay2
categories::  UGens>Delays


Description::

Delays the input by 1 sample.


classmethods::

method::ar, kr

argument::in
Input signal.

argument::mul
Output will be multiplied by this value.

argument::add
This value will be added to the output.

